data.description: No HOA, RV Parking, 3 -bedroom 2-bath remodeled home located in Vintage Vegas Arts District. The moment you step inside, you're embraced by an open floor plan, unveiling a kitchen with custom cabinets and a convenient breakfast bar. The true enchantment awaits in your backyard, a hidden oasis with a covered patio, offering a haven for relaxation and entertainment. Venture upstairs, and you'll be captivated by the breathtaking views. You're .7 miles from the Main Street Brewery District, .7 miles from Strat, 1.4 miles from The Fremont Experience and within easy reach of many Las Vegas attractions. Call for a private showing.
